<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <tr>
        <td style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
          <h1 style="color: #c41c1c; font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">E-MAX Worldwide Express</h1>
          <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 32px 0;">Smart Quote System</p>

          <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 0 0 32px 0;" />

          <p style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">안녕하세요, <%= @user.name || @user.email %> 님</p>
          <p style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
            Hello, <%= @user.name || @user.email %>
          </p>

          <p style="color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
            아래 버튼을 클릭하시면 비밀번호 없이 로그인하실 수 있습니다.<br />
            Click the button below to log in without a password.
          </p>

          <p style="color: #888; font-size: 13px; margin: 0 0 32px 0;">
            이 링크는 <strong><%= @expires_in %></strong> 동안 유효하며 1회만 사용 가능합니다.<br />
            This link is valid for <strong><%= @expires_in %></strong> and can only be used once.
          </p>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin: 0 0 32px 0;">
            <%= link_to "로그인 / Log In", @magic_url, style: "display: inline-block; background-color: #c41c1c; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold;" %>
          </div>

          <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
            버튼이 작동하지 않으면 아래 링크를 브라우저에 직접 붙여넣으세요:<br />
            If the button doesn't work, copy and paste the link below into your browser:
          </p>
          <p style="color: #c41c1c; font-size: 12px; word-break: break-all; margin: 0 0 32px 0;">
            <%= @magic_url %>
          </p>

          <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 0 0 16px 0;" />

          <p style="color: #aaa; font-size: 12px; margin: 0;">
            본인이 요청하지 않은 경우 이 이메일을 무시하세요.<br />
            If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
